<li id="cite_note-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/69276/Body-and-Soul/original-print-info.html">"Original Print Information: Body and Soul (1931)."</a> <i>Turner Classic movies</i>. Retrieved: August 10, 2014.</span></li>
</ol>
</div>
